from trades

%sql
select trade_date, substr(trade_time,12,2) as hour, substr(trade_time,15,2) as min,sum(price*volume) as total_value, sum(volume) as volume, avg(price) as avg_price
from trades 
group by trade_date, substr(trade_time,12,2), substr(trade_time,15,2)
order by trade_date, hour, min
